@startuml
title GenClaw 最简架构图

left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName "Microsoft YaHei"
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam ArrowColor #475569
skinparam component {
  BorderColor #334155
  BackgroundColor #F8FAFC
}
skinparam database {
  BorderColor #92400E
  BackgroundColor #FFF7ED
}
skinparam cloud {
  BorderColor #1D4ED8
  BackgroundColor #EFF6FF
}

actor "用户" as User

component "CLI\n接收 prompt / 命令" as CLI
component "编排层\n驱动生成流程" as Pipeline
component "认知层\n理解需求并生成 CanvasPlan" as Agent
component "代码画布层\n生成 canvas 源码并渲染 sketch.png" as Renderer
component "图像生成层\n根据 sketch 生成 final.png" as Generator
component "审查层\n检查结构与最终图像" as Reviewer

cloud "外部模型与检索服务\nLLM / 图像模型 / Search" as Services

database "运行产物\nrequest.json\nplan.json\ncanvas.*\nsketch.png\nfinal.png\nreview.json\ntrace.jsonl" as Artifacts

User --> CLI : 输入需求
CLI --> Pipeline : 启动 run
Pipeline --> Agent : conceptualize
Agent --> Services : 调用 LLM / 可选检索
Agent --> Renderer : CanvasPlan
Renderer --> Generator : sketch.png
Generator --> Services : 图像生成 / 编辑
Generator --> Reviewer : final.png
Reviewer --> Services : 可选 VLM 审查
Reviewer --> Pipeline : 通过 / 需要修订
Pipeline --> Renderer : 未通过且有预算时重画

Pipeline --> Artifacts : 全流程写入
Agent --> Artifacts : plan.json
Renderer --> Artifacts : canvas.* / sketch.png
Generator --> Artifacts : final.png
Reviewer --> Artifacts : review.json

note bottom of Agent
  CanvasPlan 是核心契约:
  认知层产出,画布层和审查层共同消费。
end note

@enduml
